Package datastructure

Comprises classes to store and exchange data internally.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    FastaEntry
    Represents the entry from a `.fasta` file.
    FeatureAnalysisEntry
    Internal representation of a reference sequence location that is subject to analysis.
    PositionStatistics
    Container class to store counts regarding different call types of one analyzed position.
    SampleAnalysisEntry
    Internal representation of a sample that is subject to analysis.
    SampleStatistics
    Container class to store counts regarding different call types of one analyzed sample.
    VariantContent
    Stores information about the content of a single genomic position of one sample relative to a reference (genetic sequence).
    VariantPositionsTable
    Major data structure to store the results of Musial.
